[p 
	"- SOME NUMBERS AND OTHER SUBLETIES:
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"A death costs 202 frames (from his explosion to his respawn)
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"The player have 48 frames of invulnerability, whereas an enemy only have 34 (bosses included expect green crazy flame)
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"The loading time when entering a place is 89 frames and go out is 96 frames.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"2'28" (8216 frames) is the time needed to obtain the "Long Sword" (hearth + golden apple + exchange + getting the sword)
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"37 is the number of fights that will take half the time compared to the axe.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"36 is the number of frames that count the use of the pause menu.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"The "Speed Shoes" makes the player 1.25 times faster.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"More than 600, it's the number of attempts made on the original hardware (SMS2) to obtain one non-fixed key drop.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"1000, it's the number of times I thank the people who makes BIZHAWK what it is!
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
